<div class="allianceSection">
	 <h4 class="header">Characteristic Species</h4>
	<div class="text"> <i>Bursera</i> <i>microphylla</i> grows as individuals or in small stands with shrubs, including <i>Ambrosia</i> <i>dumosa</i>, <i>Encelia</i> <i>farinosa</i>, <i>Hyptis</i> <i>emoryi</i> and <i>Larrea</i> <i>tridentata</i>. </div>
</div>

        
	
<div class="allianceSection">
	 <h4 class="header">Vegetation Layers</h4>
	<div class="text"> Trees < 8 m; canopy is open and emergent. Shrub layer is open to intermittent. </div>
</div>

        
